review_text: I loved working with Mark Crook from start to finish for a commercial property we purchased a few months back.  He was very professional and knowledgeable and when we closed, he brought by a wonderful congratulatory box of chocolates. What a nice touch! His customer service is first class. Please see him for all of your commercial lending needs!
Not just good, but excellent service is provided at this bank.  This the better of the two TSB's in close proximity in Thomaston.
